	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Documentation",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Security schemes",
					"item": [
						{
							"name": "OAuth 2.0",
							"item": [],
							"description": "## Overview\n\nSupported grant types:\n\n- `client_credentials`\n    \n- `password`\n    \n- `authorization_code`\n    \n\nAuthorization URI example: `https://dev-cloud.acronis.com/api/2/idp/authorize`  \nAccess token URI example: `https://dev-cloud.acronis.com/api/2/idp/token`\n\n## Request parameters\n\n### Headers\n\n| Name | Description |\n| --- | --- |\n| `Authorization` | (Required) Usual OAuth2 access token  <br>  <br>**Type**: String  <br>**Pattern**: ^Bearer \\[0-9a-zA-Z-._\\~+/\\]\\*=$ |\n\n## Scopes\n\n- `urn:acronis.com::platform-app-mgr::metadata_reader`\n    \n- `urn:acronis.com::platform-app-mgr::error_reporter`\n    \n- `urn:acronis.com::platform-app-mgr::custom_callback_executor`\n    \n- `urn:acronis.com::platform-app-mgr::application_enabler`\n    \n- `urn:acronis.com::platform-app-mgr::service_users`\n    \n- `urn:acronis.com::platform-app-mgr::enablement_status`"
						}
					]
				}
			],
			"auth": {
				"type": "noauth"
			}
		},
		{
			"name": "/application/{vendor_app_code}",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "/service_user:login",
					"item": [
						{
							"name": "Log in using service user account",
							"event": [
								{
									"listen": "test",
									"script": {
										"exec": [
											"const CODE_RESPONSE_MAP = {",
											"    200: {",
											"        mediaType: 'text/html',",
											"    },",
											"};",
											"const STATUS_CODES = [200];",
											"",
											"const { code, responseSize } = pm.response;",
											"",
											"pm.test(`Response status code is one of: ${STATUS_CODES.join(', ')}.`, () => {",
											"    pm.expect(code).to.be.oneOf(STATUS_CODES);",
											"",
											"    const { mediaType, schema } = CODE_RESPONSE_MAP[code];",
											"    ((mediaType || responseSize) ? pm.test : pm.test.skip)(\"Content-type is as expected for the status code.\", () => {",
											"        pm.expect(pm.response.headers.get(\"Content-Type\")).to.include(mediaType);",
											"    });",
											"",
											"    ((mediaType && (mediaType === 'application/json' || mediaType.endsWith('+json'))) ? pm.test : pm.test.skip)(\"JSON response is valid according to the API contract.\", () => {",
											"        pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.jsonSchema(schema);",
											"    });",
											"});"
										],
										"type": "text/javascript",
										"packages": {}
									}
								}
							],
							"request": {
								"method": "GET",
								"header": [],
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{base_url}}/application/:vendor_app_code/service_user:login?tenant_id=4f74fd57-fd72-4a86-9f6b-f3b201ca9cc4&purpose=login&external_id=demo_analyst",
									"host": [
										"{{base_url}}"
									],
									"path": [
										"application",
										":vendor_app_code",
										"service_user:login"
									],
									"query": [
										{
											"key": "tenant_id",
											"value": "4f74fd57-fd72-4a86-9f6b-f3b201ca9cc4",
											"description": "(Required) Tenant ID for the requested login.\n\n**Type**: String\n**Pattern**: ^[0-9a-fA-F]{8}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{12}$"
										},
										{
											"key": "purpose",
											"value": "login",
											"description": "(Required) Mandatory purpose string explaining the reason for the requested login.\n\n**Type**: String"
										},
										{
											"key": "external_id",
											"value": "demo_analyst",
											"description": "(Required) External user id.\n\n**Type**: String"
										}
									],
									"variable": [
										{
											"key": "vendor_app_code",
											"value": ""
										}
									]
								}
							},
							"response": [
								{
									"name": "200",
									"originalRequest": {
										"method": "GET",
										"header": [],
										"url": {
											"raw": "{{base_url}}/service_user:login",
											"host": [
												"{{base_url}}"
											],
											"path": [
												"service_user:login"
											]
										}
									},
									"status": "OK",
									"code": 200,
									"_postman_previewlanguage": "html",
									"header": [
										{
											"key": "Content-Type",
											"value": "text/html"
										}
									],
									"cookie": [],
									"body": ""
								}
							]
						}
					]
				}
			]
		}
